      "width": 250,
      "x": -1350,
      "y": 1550
    },
    {
      "height": 80,
      "id": "event_qi_heng_fails",
      "text": "齐衡提亲失败\nDue to family pressure, Qi Heng's proposal fails, breaking their hearts.",
