      "width": 250,
      "x": -1050,
      "y": 1550
    },
    {
      "height": 80,
      "id": "event_molan_scheme",
      "text": "墨兰的诡计\nSheng Molan schemes to marry Liang Han, shaming the Sheng family.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "x": -750,
      "y": 1550
    },
    {
      "height": 80,
      "id": "event_gu_proposal",
      "text": "顾廷烨求亲\nGu Tingye, now a powerful general, lays an elaborate plan to marry Minglan.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "x": -450,
      "y": 1550
    },
    {
      "height": 80,
      "id": "event_household_manage",
      "text": "管家立威\nMinglan skillfully manages the complex household and deals with difficult relatives.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 150,
      "y": 1550
    },
    {
      "height": 80,
      "id": "event_vs_xiaoqinshi",
      "text": "对抗小秦氏\nContinuous struggle against the schemes of her stepmother-in-law, Xiao Qinshi.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 450,
      "y": 1550
    },
    {
      "height": 80,
      "id": "event_justice",
      "text": "明兰伸冤\nA pregnant Minglan seeks justice for her husband, confronting the empress and officials.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 1050,
      "y": 1550
    },
    {
      "height": 80,
      "id": "event_coup_return",
      "text": "平乱归来\nGu Tingye returns triumphantly after quelling a rebellion, clearing his name.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 1350,
      "y": 1550
    },
    {
      "height": 80,
      "id": "event_happy_ending",
      "text": "幸福结局\nAll antagonists receive their comeuppance. Minglan and Gu Tingye live a happy, peaceful life.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 1650,
      "y": 1550
    },
    {
      "height": 80,
      "id": "event_exile",
      "text": "顾廷烨被贬\nGu Tingye is framed by his enemies and the emperor, and is exiled.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 750,
      "y": 1550
    }
  ]
